name: streamz_ext
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "streamz_ext" %}
{% set version = "0.2.1" %}
{% set sha256 = "b8cc9549095bd76d47160438503ff886d2f5339264867b6c429fba29ae811237" %}

package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  fn: {{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  url: https://github.com/xpdAcq/{{ name }}/releases/download/{{ version }}/{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: {{ sha256 }}

build:
  noarch: python
  number: 0
  script: python -m pip install --no-deps --ignore-installed . 

requirements:
  build:
    - python
    - pip
  run:
    - python
    - toolz
    - tornado
    - streamz
    - distributed


test:
  imports:
    - streamz
    - streamz.core
    - streamz.dask

about:
  home: https://github.com/xpdAcq/streamz_ext
  license: BSD-3-Clause
  license_family: BSD
  license_file: LICENSE
  summary: 'Extension of Streamz'
  dev_url: https://github.com/xpdAcq/streamz_ext

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - CJ-Wright
